
notes

Cross-site scripting enable

http://enable-cors.org/
Have to put this in /etc/httpd/conf/httpd.conf:

<Directory /var/www/html/docshack>
  AllowOverride All
</Directory>


and this .htaccess file in /var/www/html/docshack
Header set Access-Control-Allow-Origin *


chmod u+s on bin/builder and html/docshack/buildabook

chmod -R s+G books and server/standalone/deployment/TopicIndex.war/Books

